- 工具类

```java
/**
 * Project Name:report
 * File Name:PdfReportM1HeaderFooter.java
 * Package Name:com.riambsoft.report.pdf
 * Date:2013-9-16上午08:59:00
 * Copyright (c) 2013, riambsoft All Rights Reserved.
